Description: Model Context Protocol server for local Ollama models
 mcp-ollama-python is a Python MCP server that exposes local Ollama
 models as tools for AI assistants (Windsurf, VS Code, Claude Desktop).
 .
 Provides utilities for:
  * Chat with local models (multi-turn, tool-calling)
  * Text generation and completions
  * Vector embeddings
  * Model management (list, pull, delete)
  * Running model inspection and process control
 .
 All operations run locally without cloud APIs.
